imdb.plot outline: 2 Girls 1 Show is a comedy series that explores internet communities and culture. Each episode focuses on a different online phenomenon (e.g. bronies, the rise of sugar dating, etc.). The show pairs real, unscripted interviews with the people behind the posts, and scripted shenanigans as the two girls run around NYC "testing" what they learned. This "research" always leads to an onstage comedy sketch, as the girls are performers. Loosely based on real life.
